whippyterm (2.3.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Numerous small fixes and enhancements
    - Added new option to clear the screen on send buffer
    - Changed default bottom panel size
    - Changed how maximize window on startup works
    - Added new option for rescanning connections
    - Fixed the binary processor field lengths of 0
    - Added version number to window title
    - Added quick jump button to send line inputs
    - Added new standard text input line to text mode
    - Added direct panel selections to session
    - Added a close button to the direct send panel
    - Added settings for if direct send panel should be open or closed
    - Added new clear screen option to clear scroll buffer
    - Added new clear screen option to clear hex panels as well
    - Added an option to clear the scroll back buffer if clear screen double pressed
    - Fixed a number of small bugs after an AI code lint
    - RTS/CTS flow control broken on Linux
    - Fixed spelling errors
    - Reworked the terminal emulation menu
    - Font rendering doesn't lineup with mouse clicks
    - Fixed sounds not playing.

