    - Changed side panels to have control together
    - Fixed a number of issues with Dark Mode
    - Fixed a problem with the DPI not drawing the panels open/close bars correctly.
    - Added error messages to the upload/download
    - Added new options to xmodem transfer
    - Changed file transfers to auto open side panel
    - Complete rewrite on auto reconnect system
    - Updated Binary HexDump to support Binary Protocol Description Standard strings
    - Added new widget WebLink for plugins
    - Reset term didn't reset colors in binary mode
    - Added function to let plugins change a widgets label
    - Added support code for columns
    - Added change property widget control
    - Added new event for text input widgets
    - Added new style picker widget
    - Added a save button to the hex panels
    - Fixed a bug where if a block of bytes came in it wouldn't add to hex panel
    - Added new out going hex panel
    - Added menu entries to open/close the panels
    - Mouse over for panels wasn't working.  Fixed
    - Added comport settings for user speeds
    - Added settings to IO Drivers
    - Added record button to bind keys
    - Changed how insert horizontal rule works
    - Added setting for tab size
    - Added new settings to the ANSI decoder
    - Added an option to add a line feed when a carriage return is received

